  <brief_title>Study to Assess the Effect of 24 Weeks of Treatment With Vildagliptin in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single-center,Double-blind,Randomised,Placebo-controlled,Parallel-group Study to Assess the Effect of 24 Weeks of Treatment With Vildagliptin on Insulin Sensitivity and Its Underlying Mechanism in Patients With T2DM Treated With Metformin</official_title>
  <sponsors>
